data.description: SELLER OFFERING $1500 CREDIT TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COSTS!  Located on a quiet cul-de-sac in Argyle Forest, this 3b/2ba home plus flex space, perfect for a playroom, office or home gym. This home features granite countertops, renovated cabinets, recessed lighting, vinyl plank flooring and bali blinds. The open floor-plan boasts beautiful natural light throughout the home! This home is truly turnkey- HVAC, water heater, and stainless-steel kitchen appliances all installed in 2022. Enjoy the privacy of your spacious backyard and screened lanai which is perfect for entertaining. Equipped with ADT Security, window/door sensors and detectors throughout and transferable with service agreement and LeafFilter gutter protection with transferable warranty.
